  "text": [
    "The fields are white;",
    "The laborers are few;",
    "Yet say the idle:",
    "There\u2019s nothing to do.",
    "Jails are crowded;",
    "In Sunday-schools few;",
    "We still complain:",
    "There\u2019s nothing to do.",
    "Drunkards are dying\u2014",
    "Your sons, it is true;",
    "Mothers\u2019 arms folded",
    "With nothing to do.",
    "Heathens are dying;",
    "Their blood falls on you;",
    "How can you people",
    "Find nothing to do?"
  ],
  "title": "Nothing to Do",
  "year": ""
}